SESSION.DESCRIPTION: This session invokes the mapping m_STG_MX_GROSS_MARGIN

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET TGT_VAL=( SELECT count(*) FROM STG_MX_GROSS_MARGIN WHERE UPDATE_TIMESTAMP= (SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_GROSS_MARGIN' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE)) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_GROSS_MARGIN' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_GROSS_MARGIN' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE ) ;
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET STATUS_YN = (CASE WHEN SRC_VAL = TGT_VAL THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END ) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_GROSS_MARGIN' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_GROSS_MARGIN' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE );

SESSION.DESCRIPTION: This session creates a parameter file based on which the staging table gets loaded with data.
SESSION.NAME: s_m_STG_MX_GM_PARAM

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
Select '[YARDSTICK.s_m_STG_MX_GROSS_MARGIN]' || CHR(10) || '$$PRV_YR_PD=' || TO_CHAR(min(day_date),'YYYYMMDD') || CHR(10) || '$$CUR_YR_PD=' ||TO_CHAR(max(day_date),'YYYYMMDD') from day_dimension where cy_year_yyyy||lpad(cy_month_num,2,'0')
in (Select case when d.cy_month_num ='1' then to_char(to_number(cy_year_yyyy) -1) else cy_year_yyyy end || case when d.cy_month_num ='1' then '12' else lpad(to_char(to_number(d.cy_month_num)-1),2,'0') end as Prev from day_dimension d where trunc(day_date) = trunc(sysdate)
union
Select d.cy_year_yyyy||lpad(d.cy_month_num,2,'0') as cur from day_dimension d where trunc(day_date) = trunc(sysdate))
order by day_date
